Package fr.dauphine.javaavance.phineloops.view

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionsDisplay
    A JPanel which contains the possible actions for a user of the graphic interface
    CheckPanel
    A Panel for the user to perform the checking action to see if the grid he played on is resolved or not
    GeneratePanel
    A JPanel which contains input fields and an action button in order for a user of the gui to generate a new grid
    GridDisplay
    This class is the panel hosting all the pieces composing a grid for a graphic display
    MainDisplay
    This class is the frame of the graphic part of the project, it shows a playable grid on the left side and the possible actions (provided by the programs package) on the right side
    PieceDisplay
    This class serves as the displayer for a piece of the grid It is a JButton which can be clicked on for interacting with the concerned piece
